#: ../../contribute.md:1
msgid "Contributing"
msgstr "贡献"

#: ../../contribute.md:3
msgid "Bugs and feature requests"
msgstr "Bug和功能请求"

#: ../../contribute.md:5
msgid ""
"Use the official repository for bugs, ideas and features requests: "
"https://github.com/Koromix/koffi"
msgstr ""
"使用官方仓库提出bug, 想法和功能请求: https://github.com/Koromix/koffi"

#: ../../contribute.md:7
msgid ""
"Please note that the source code is not in this repository, instead it "
"lives in a monorepo: https://github.com/Koromix/rygel/ (in the "
"*src/koffi* subdirectory)."
msgstr ""
"请注意, 源代码不在这个仓库, 相反它在一个monorepo中: https://github.com/Koromix/rygel/(在*src/koffi*子目录下)"

