#: ../../contribute.md:53
msgid "Running tests"
msgstr "执行测试"

#: ../../contribute.md:55
msgid ""
"Koffi is tested on multiple architectures using emulated (accelerated "
"when possible) QEMU machines. First, you need to install qemu packages, "
"such as `qemu-system` (or even `qemu-system-gui`) on Ubuntu."
msgstr ""
"Koffi使用QEMU虚拟机(以及可能的硬件加速)在多个架构下经过测试. 首先, 你需要安装qemu包, 例如Ubuntu上的`qemu-system`(亦或是`qemu-system-gui`)."

#: ../../contribute.md:57
msgid ""
"These machines are not included directly in this repository (for license "
"and size reasons), but they are available here: "
"https://koromix.dev/files/machines/"
msgstr ""
"这些虚拟机没有直接包含在仓库中(出于license和大小考虑), 但是它们可以在这里获取: https://koromix.dev/files/machines/"

