#: ../../contribute.md:67
msgid ""
"Note that the machine disk content may change each time the machine runs,"
" so the checksum test will fail once a machine has been used at least "
"once."
msgstr ""
"注意, 设备的磁盘内容在每次运行时可能会变更, 因此checksum测试在设备被多次使用时会失败."

