msgid "And now you can run the tests with:"
msgstr "现在你可以通过下列命令执行测试:"

#: ../../contribute.md:75
msgid ""
"And be patient, this can be pretty slow for emulated machines. The Linux "
"machines have and use ccache to build Koffi, so subsequent build steps "
"will get much more tolerable."
msgstr ""
"请耐心, 对于虚拟机这可能会相当慢. Linux设备有且使用了ccache来构建Koffi, 因此后续的构建步骤耗时已经可以接受了."

#: ../../contribute.md:77
msgid ""
