"start the machines ahead of time and run the tests multiple times "
"instead:"
msgstr ""
"默认情况下, 每次测试虚拟机会被打开和关闭. 但是你可以提前打开设备并且直接多次执行测试:"

#: ../../contribute.md:86
msgid "You can also restrict the test to a subset of machines:"
msgstr "你也可以限制只测试一部分设备:"

#: ../../contribute.md:98
msgid ""
"Finally, you can join a running machine with SSH with the following "
"shortcut, if you need to do some debugging or any other manual procedure:"
msgstr ""
"最后, 如果你需要做调试或其它手动操作, 可以使用下列快捷命令通过SSH登录一个执行中的设备."

#: ../../contribute.md:104
msgid ""
"Each machine is configured to run a VNC server available locally, which "
"you can use to access the display, using KRDC or any other compatible "
"viewer. Use the `info` command to get the VNC port."
msgstr ""
"每个设备都被配置了本地的VNC服务, 因此你可以使用KRDC或其它兼容的工具查看屏幕. 使用`info`命令来获得VNC端口."

#: ../../contribute.md:110
msgid "Code style"
msgstr "代码风格"

#: ../../contribute.md:112
msgid ""
"Koffi is programmed in a mix of C++ and assembly code (architecture-"
"specific code). It uses [node-addon-api](https://github.com/nodejs/node-"
"addon-api) (C++ N-API wrapper) to interact with Node.js."
msgstr ""
"Koffi时一个C++和汇编(针对特定架构的代码)混合的项目. 它使用[node-addon-api](https://github.com/nodejs/node-"
"addon-api)(C++ N-API封装)来和Node.js交互."

#: ../../contribute.md:114
msgid ""
"My personal preference goes to a rather C-like C++ style, with careful "
"use of templates (mainly for containers) and little object-oriented "
"programming. I strongly prefer tagged unions and code locality over "
"inheritance and virtual methods. Exceptions are disabled."
msgstr ""
"我(@Koromix)个人倾向于C风格的C++, 以及小心使用的模板(主要用于容器)和少量的面向对象开发. "
"相比于继承和虚函数, 我(@Koromix)更愿意使用带标记的联合体以及局部代码. 禁用了异常."

